## Limitations

The report is based on available data as of April 2025 and may not capture subsequent developments in the used car market. Additionally, the analysis relies on secondary sources, which may have inherent biases or limitations in their reporting. Further research and data collection would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the market dynamics.